Global Artificial Disc Market Insights
Artificial Disc Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 6.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Artificial Disc Market Overview
The global Artificial Disc Market is expected to reach USD 5.6 billion by 2028, with a CAGR of 7.8% during the forecast period. The increasing prevalence of spinal disorders and advancements in medical technology are major drivers for the growth of the market. Artificial disc replacement is seen as a viable alternative to spinal fusion surgeries, as it helps maintain natural spine movement and improves recovery time. North America leads the market, owing to high healthcare spending and technological innovations. Europe and the Asia-Pacific region are also witnessing significant growth due to rising awareness and improving healthcare infrastructure.

